div.p:
Besides, the Ships could not furnish the Army with more Men or Victuals:
wherefore I understand not in what Respect his going up was necessary;
and yet the Fleet must have endured many Hazards to this little purpose.

The Purser of her was taken, and by Threats compell'd to tell of another
of their Company behind, that had Order to fall with that Island;
and gave us such particular Advertisement, that indeed she fell to be ours.
